    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 58-61.</p><p>Expert Hunter (5.5e)</p><p>5.5e. Also at 21st level, your skill in hunting your enemies has deepened. You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls against targets marked by your Hunter’s Mark. In addition, you gain an extra use of your Hunter’s Mark, as shown in the Favored Enemy column in the Legendary Ranger table.</p></div>",
